Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}my life I trade in for your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:07.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向かず羽ばたけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:15.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この想いを運んで　あの空を飛んでく
